Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.37,0:00:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到羅德斯島
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.50,0:00:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼緊接著\N就請觀賞第二部份吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,~歡迎來到羅德斯島~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.90,0:00:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要過去嗎…掉下去就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.34,0:00:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先請吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.78,0:00:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦?好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.05,0:00:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮絲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.06,0:00:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.99,0:00:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿嘿…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子，真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.29,0:00:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見習騎士和他愉快的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.76,0:01:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老話，快把餅乾交出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.63,0:01:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不交出來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.70,0:01:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把橋切斷讓你們掉下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.55,0:01:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.98,0:01:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.74,0:01:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是在這噴火的話\N也會燒斷吊橋的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.95,0:01:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考慮的如何?\N兩選一，要選哪邊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不甘心，還是交出餅乾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先以妮絲的安全考量為第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.82,0:01:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，史派克
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.86,0:01:26.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自由騎士潘恩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.80,0:01:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…走的好累喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.07,0:01:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，殺出個程咬金的潘恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.60,0:01:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來阻礙我嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.27,0:01:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來救我們的吧，潘恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.24,0:01:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想起了重要的事了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.11,0:01:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將這個交給史派克…啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳情且待下回分解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.32,0:01:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得再看喔
